FBIS4-44315 "drweu125_i_94006" FBIS-WEU-94-125 Daily Report 28 Jun 1994 FRANCE Juppe Meets Yemeni Foreign Minister 28 Jun Juppe Meets Yemeni Foreign Minister 28 Jun JN2806185994 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 1700 GMT 28 Jun 94 JN2806185994 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Text] [Yemeni] Foreign Minister Muhammad Salim Basindwah met in Paris today with his French counterpart, Alain Juppe. They reviewed the developments of the situation in the Republic of Yemen. During the meeting, the French foreign minister stressed the need for a cease-fire and the need to resolve the crisis in our country within the framework of maintaining unity and democracy. He stressed that unity and democracy are the Yemeni people's option, which has been realized by their own free will.
